<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.RenderPluginEnumerator.AddPluginByPath" Title="AddPluginByPath method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.RenderPluginEnumerator">RenderPluginEnumerator</PageRef> ->
    AddPluginByPath
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>AddPluginByPath</TypeRef> method loads a single plugin library, resolves its exported <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.GetCobaltAPIVersion">GetCobaltAPIVersion</PageRef> function, checks that the plugin was built against a compatible Cobalt Renderer API version, resolves its exported <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.GetRendererPlugin">GetRendererPlugin</PageRef> function, and adds every renderer implementation exported by that library.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[SuccessToken AddPluginByPath(const std::filesystem::path& pluginFilePath);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="const std::filesystem::path&amp;" Name="pluginFilePath">
          The plugin library file to load.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="SuccessToken!cobalt.graphics.SuccessToken">
        True if at least one renderer implementation was added from the library; otherwise false.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
